      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Even worse, some hackers have been able to take over certain systems on a vehicle while it’s traveling down the road. That’s scary since that kind of move could cause you to crash, etc.",
