          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Some people might think this technology is great since it would mean criminals can’t run from the police. And while we admit that does seem attractive, we also know that such power in the control of a government could easily be used for less-than-pure motives.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
